---
title: "invalidateOrders (Payment Abstraction V2 - GPV2CompatibleAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_access: onlyRole(ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE)
    q_check_access --> q_iter: for orderUid in orderUids
    q_iter --> q_invalidate: i_gpV2Settlement.invalidateOrder(orderUid)
    q_invalidate --> q_iter: next order
    q_iter --> [*]: all orders invalidated

    note right of q_invalidate
        INV-001: Only ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE (via WorkflowRouter) can invalidate CowSwap orders
        INV-002: Delegates to GPv2Settlement contract for on-chain order cancellation
    end note
